[11:53:08.181] [INFO ]     Here is a detailed comparison of **NovaLens Professional** and **Business** tiers:
    
    | Feature | Professional | Business |
    |---------|--------------|----------|
    | **Price** | $99/month per user<br/>($990/year per user - 17% discount) | $499/month per user<br/>($4,990/year per user - 17% discount) |
    | **Predictions** | 10,000/month | 100,000/month |
    | **User Seats** | 1 seat | 10 seats included<br/>($299/month per additional seat) |
    | **Model Deployments** | 5 active deployments | Unlimited deployments |
    | **Custom Model Training** | Not included | Included |
    | **Batch Processing** | Not included | Included |
    | **API Rate Limit** | 10 requests/second | 100 requests/second |
    | **Data Retention** | 90 days | 365 days |
    | **Support** | Email support<br/>24-hour response time | Priority email + phone support<br/>4-hour response time |
    | **Account Management** | Self-service | Dedicated account manager |
    | **SLA** | Standard | 99.9% uptime guarantee |
    | **Security** | Standard encryption | Advanced features: audit logs, SSO/SAML, VPC deployment |
    | **Onboarding** | Self-guided documentation | Personalized onboarding session |
    
    **Key Differences:**
    
    **Professional** is designed for individual developers or small teams getting started with computer vision. It provides access to all core NovaLens models (object detection, classification, segmentation, OCR) with moderate usage limits.
    
    **Business** is built for teams and organizations running computer vision in production. The 10x higher prediction quota, unlimited deployments, and custom model training capabilities support larger-scale applications. The enhanced support, security, and SLA make it suitable for mission-critical use cases.
    
    Both tiers include access to the NovaLens web platform, API, mobile SDKs, and pre-trained models. For enterprise needs beyond these tiers (unlimited predictions, on-premise deployment, or custom contracts), NovaLens Enterprise is available with custom pricing.
    
    *Pricing current as of January 2024. For the most up-to-date details, see the official NovaLens pricing page.*
